Sentencas: Electrolysis behaviors have been investigated based on ceria-based composite electrolytes and fuel cells.
Titulo: Electrolysis studies based on ceria-based composites

Sentencas: The results showed that both proton and oxygen ion conduction exist in the ceria-based composite electrolytes resulting in high current outputs in both fuel cell and electrolysis operations.
Titulo: Electrolysis studies based on ceria-based composites

Sentencas: Corresponding to high current output in the electrolysis cell, a high hydrogen production can be expected.
Titulo: Electrolysis studies based on ceria-based composites

Sentencas: This work has first demonstrated the ceria-based composite electrolyte used for electrolysis process.
Titulo: Electrolysis studies based on ceria-based composites
